Class AbstractSurvivalFilter

java.lang.Object

      com.xtructure.xevolution.evolution.impl.AbstractSurvivalFilter
All Implemented Interfaces:
EvolutionObject, SurvivalFilter
Direct Known Subclasses:
AbstractNEATSurvivalFilter, SurvivalFilterImpl
public abstract class AbstractSurvivalFilter
extends AbstractEvolutionObject
implements SurvivalFilter

AbstractSurvivalFilter implements the SurvivalFilter interface, where it marks dead Genomes in a Population.

It marks all Genomes for death, so that every generation contains only children of the previous generation.

Author:
Luis Guimbarda
